    "body": "MKL includes `fftw3` wrappers. So `intel-parallel-studio-package` should also provide the virtual package for `fftw-api`. \r\n\r\nMy current workaround is in `packages.yaml`:\r\n\r\n```\r\nfftw:\r\n   paths: /opt/software/common/intel/compilers_and_libraries_2019.4.243/linux/mkl/\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd it seems to work... \r\n",
